'''娜歐蜜·芳納·吉倫荷'''（'''Naomi Foner Gyllenhaal'''，本名'''Naomi Achs'''，{{bd|1946年|3月15日|}}），是一位出生於美國[[紐約市|紐約市]]的[[猶太|猶太]]裔編劇<ref>{{cite web|first=Gerard|last=Gilbert|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/features/maggie-gyllenhaals-role-in-bbc2-spy-drama-the-honourable-woman-sounds-like-the-perfect-fit-even-with-9580264.html|title=Maggie Gyllenhaal on her new role in BBC2 spy drama The Honourable Woman|work=The Independent|date=July 2, 2014|accessdate=April 24, 2018|archive-date=2018-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180424135927/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/features/maggie-gyllenhaals-role-in-bbc2-spy-drama-the-honourable-woman-sounds-like-the-perfect-fit-even-with-9580264.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://forward.com/schmooze/202663/naomi-foner-on-very-good-girls-and-her-famous-chil/|title=Naomi Foner on ‘Very Good Girls’ and Her Famous Children|author=|date=July 24, 2014|work=|newspaper=The Forward|accessdate=May 20, 2018|quote=Naomi Foner: "I certainly think of myself as Jewish and I tried to bring up my children think of themselves as Jews."|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617220033/https://forward.com/schmooze/202663/naomi-foner-on-very-good-girls-and-her-famous-chil/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1989年，憑借電影《[[不設限通緝|不設限通緝]]》（''Running on Empty''）提名[[第61屆奧斯卡金像獎|第61屆奧斯卡金像獎]]最佳原創劇本獎<ref>{{cite web|title=Jamie Lee Curtis and Naomi Foner on What It Means to Be ‘Very Good Girls’|url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/jamie-lee-curtis-and-naomi-foner-on-what-it-means-to-be-very-good-girls|work=The Daily Beast|date=July 25, 2014|accessdate=April 22, 2018|archive-date=2021-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512092220/https://www.thedailybeast.com/jamie-lee-curtis-and-naomi-foner-on-what-it-means-to-be-very-good-girls}}</ref>。

吉倫荷為多部電影編寫過[[劇本|劇本]]，包括《[[不設限通緝|不設限通緝]]》（''Running on Empty''）、《[[生母養母的戰爭|生母養母的戰爭]]》（''Losing Isaiah''），以及近期的《[[拼出真愛|拼出真愛]]》（''Bee Season''）。她同時也是電視影集《''{{le|The Electric Company}}》其中兩季的協同製作人。

== 個人生活 ==
吉倫荷在紐約市的一個[[猶太人|猶太人]]家庭中長大<ref>{{cite web|first=Susan|last=Josephs|title=‘Bee’ Spells Family D-y-s-f-u-n-c-t-i-o-n-a-l|url=http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/12194/|work=Jewish Journal|date=November 10, 2005|accessdate=April 22, 2018|archive-date=2018-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180624175909/http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/12194/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2004/10/31/movies/writing-her-way-back-to-the-family-business.html|title=Writing Her Way Back to the Family Business|accessdate=April 22, 2018|author=|date=October 31, 2004|work=The New York Times|publisher=|quote=Ms. Gyllenhaal grew up in a family of "high-achieving New York Jews," she said.|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617223051/https://www.nytimes.com/2004/10/31/movies/writing-her-way-back-to-the-family-business.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Janet|last=Christie|title=Maggie Gyllenhaal: Acting for self-discovery|url=https://www.scotsman.com/lifestyle/culture/film/maggie-gyllenhaal-acting-for-self-discovery-1-3452677|work=The Scotsman|date=June 22, 2014|accessdate=April 22, 2018|archive-date=2018-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180422202128/https://www.scotsman.com/lifestyle/culture/film/maggie-gyllenhaal-acting-for-self-discovery-1-3452677|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/ads/beeseason/articles_naomi1.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2007-05-07 |archive-date=2008-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080213014944/http://www.nytimes.com/ads/beeseason/articles_naomi1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，她的父母都是醫生<ref>{{cite web|first=Naomi|last=Pfefferman|url=http://jewishjournal.com/current_edition/131226/|title=Maggie Gyllenhaal stars in SundanceTV’s “The Honorable Woman”|work=Jewish Journal|date=July 23, 2014|accessdate=April 24, 2018|archive-date=2018-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180424135239/http://jewishjournal.com/current_edition/131226/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她就讀於紐約的柏納大學（Barnard College），是一所隸屬於[[哥倫比亞大學|哥倫比亞大學]]的分校。她畢業於該學校的英語系。

她曾與[[電影導演|電影導演]][[史帝芬·吉倫荷|史帝芬·吉倫荷]]在工作上進行合作，之後兩人正式步入禮堂。這對夫妻育有兩名孩子，分別是[[演員|演員]][[瑪姬·吉倫荷|瑪姬·吉倫荷]]和[[傑克·吉倫荷|傑克·吉倫荷]]。她的前夫是一位[[歷史學家|歷史學家]]和哥倫比亞大學教授艾瑞克·方納（Eric Foner）<ref>http://www.columbiaspectator.com/vnews/display.v/ART/2006/02/09/43eaef7bb496f?in_archive=1{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

2006年10月3日，吉倫荷首次成為祖母，她的女兒和其未婚夫在[[紐約|紐約]]產下一名女嬰，名為 Ramona Sarsgaard。

